headline: AutoZone (AZO) Announces Executive Leadership Changes as Key Officers Prepare to Retire
summary: AutoZone (AZO) recently saw executive changes with the retirement announcements of Bill Hackney and Rick Smith, reaching key leadership milestones. Over the last quarter, the company's share price rose 12%, a notable performance amid the broader market ascent. This price move, potentially supported by leadership continuity efforts, contrasted with the tech sector downturn.
